e? Don't give up in the waiting, don't grow weary in the fight, God is standing with His children and He's calling you to rise. Don't stop now, stay the course, He is with you. Blow your horn. Tell that wall you're coming down, tell that fear it's breaking now, tell that doubt you've lost your ground. Blow your horn, let it ring out, tell that wall I've got a song, tell that wall my God is strong. Tell that wall you won't last long, blow your horn, keep marching on. So blow your horn, let the trumpet sound, if you're staring at a wall, it's coming down. God leads the way, so keep marching on, if faith is all you've got, then blow your horn. So blow your horn, this is your moment now, God is making every broken strong or bold. He leads the way, so keep holding on, your victory may be one more step. So blow your horn, blow your horn, blow your horn, keep marching on, blow your horn. The wall won't hold for long."}